body:
I was unable to patch the game (estimated 24 hours to download the patch), uninstalled, and tried downloading the installer. I had the same problem. The download was crawling and I had to restart it multiple times. Likewise the patcher crashed when I tried to reinstall from an old installer. My Internet is running fine for every other site. Has there been an issue with Riot's servers or is my ISP (Mediacom) doing something sketchy directed at Riot? I get the same problems attempting to download League on a computer on which it has never been installed.

I was able to download the Hextech Repair Tool at a reasonable rate...however it has been stuck trying to download the installer for the last hour or so.

